In the Matter of the Application of John O. Nelson for an Order Directing the Board of Elections of the City of New York to Reject the Petition of George Dyson Friou for Nomination as Candidate for the Republican Party for the Thirty-ninth Aldermanic District of the City of New York.

Motion to dispense with printing of record on appeal denied. Present — Rich, Young, Kapper and Hagarty, JJ.; Manning, J., absent. *867Nominating Petition of John O. Nelson, Petitioner, and Place His Name on the Ballot of the Republican Party as Candidate for the Thirty-ninth Aldermanie District in the City of New York.
